; Regression test for issue #742: ledger stats ignores -p until (BZ#742)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/742
;
; The stats command should respect the --end (or -p until) date filter,
; but currently it ignores it and reports statistics for ALL postings
; regardless of the specified period. The reg command correctly filters.

2014/01/01 Opening Balance
    Assets:Checking    $1000.00
    Equity:Opening

2014/06/15 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

2014/12/31 Year End
    Expenses:Misc    $25.00
    Assets:Checking

; With --end 2014/07/01, stats should show only 2 payees, 3 accounts, 4 postings
; (excluding the 2014/12/31 "Year End" transaction), but it still shows all 3
; payees, 4 accounts, and 6 postings — demonstrating the bug.
test stats --end 2014/07/01
Time period: 14-Jan-01 to 14-Dec-31 (364 days)

  Files these postings came from:
    $FILE

  Unique payees:               3
  Unique accounts:             4

  Number of postings:          6 (0.016 per day)
  Uncleared postings:          6

  Days since last post:     4102
  Posts in last 7 days:        0
  Posts in last 30 days:       0
  Posts seen this month:       0
end test
